    <div data-cid="3329577">
        <div class="main review-item" id="3329577">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/liudabei/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u41734277-3.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/liudabei/" class="name">刘大北</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2010-06-13" class="main-meta">2010-06-13 15:25:14</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3329577/">本格派推理小说的翘楚  之一</a></h2>

                <div id="review_3329577_short" class="review-short" data-rid="3329577">
                    <div class="short-content">

                            有的评论家甚至称悲剧系列（X的悲剧、Y的悲剧、Z的悲剧、哲瑞 雷恩的最后一案)是推理小说史上最伟大的作品。读完其第一部《X的悲剧》后，谈谈我个人的感想。首先这是一部纯而又纯的本格派推理小说。整个案件按时间顺序叙述，每个人干了什么，每个线索都交代得很清楚。如果...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3329577-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_3329577_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_3329577_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

